data.description: Home is nestled on just under an acre, split floor plan. NO CARPET! Engineered wood throughout except in wet areas. Large living area for entertaining, spacious primary bedroom, 4th room currently being used as an office, Kitchen equipped with all major appliances including a pantry. Relax and enjoy the quiet serenity this home has to offer on either covered front or back porches.
